697
00:31:34,500 --> 00:31:35,430
You call again.

698
00:31:36,940 --> 00:31:37,860
No.

699
00:32:07,460 --> 00:32:09,900
I'm not lucky enough

700
00:32:12,740 --> 00:32:14,300
