737
00:34:04,100 --> 00:34:05,380
This is your lucky year!

738
00:34:05,380 --> 00:34:06,460
You'll always profit!

739
00:34:06,460 --> 00:34:07,300
Really?

740
00:34:07,860 --> 00:34:09,980
I have techniques and you have luck.

741
00:34:09,980 --> 00:34:10,980
Will you invest more?

742
00:34:11,780 --> 00:34:13,580
Yes! No problem. I'll invest.

743
00:34:13,580 --> 00:34:15,340
If you're short of money, tell me.

744
00:34:15,860 --> 00:34:16,980
I'll lend you some.

745
00:34:16,980 --> 00:34:17,820
Ok.

746
00:34:26,180 --> 00:34:27,420
Join the army?

747
00:34:27,620 --> 00:34:28,940
Xiaonian is temporarily transferred

748
00:34:28,940 --> 00:34:30,100
