782
00:35:52,460 --> 00:35:53,740
Isn't it too much?

783
00:35:53,740 --> 00:35:55,180
Didn't you bargain?

784
00:35:56,460 --> 00:35:58,540
Well, give the money if you want.

785
00:35:58,540 --> 00:35:59,900
