815
00:37:04,500 --> 00:37:05,540
I can learn there, too.

816
00:37:05,540 --> 00:37:07,220
You know nothing about the society.

817
00:37:07,460 --> 00:37:09,340
When you're out there alone,

818
00:37:09,340 --> 00:37:10,260
