821
00:37:12,260 --> 00:37:13,260
I'm young.

822
00:37:13,260 --> 00:37:14,940
That's my advantage. I can learn.

823
00:37:17,740 --> 00:37:18,580
Besides,

824
00:37:19,260 --> 00:37:21,300
Mark promised me

825
00:37:21,300 --> 00:37:23,340
