827
00:37:25,900 --> 00:37:28,500
Yangyang, can you finish high school?

828
00:37:28,500 --> 00:37:29,460
In the future, if you...

829
00:37:29,460 --> 00:37:30,860
I don't bother about the future.

830
00:37:30,860 --> 00:37:31,730
I can't wait.

831
00:37:31,730 --> 00:37:32,740
