832
00:37:35,020 --> 00:37:37,220
Anyway, I've grown up.

833
00:37:37,660 --> 00:37:38,940
I can choose my own future.

834
00:37:38,940 --> 00:37:40,100
You're still under 18

835
00:37:40,100 --> 00:37:41,100
and you aren't an adult.

836
00:37:46,620 --> 00:37:49,620
He just has his mother's temper.

837
00:37:49,620 --> 00:37:50,580
When he's stubborn,

838
00:37:50,580 --> 00:37:52,140
