(Huainan Beef Soup)

844
00:38:36,740 --> 00:38:38,060
Mom has been there.

845
00:38:38,060 --> 00:38:39,380
I totally understand you.

846
00:38:39,620 --> 00:38:41,260
The world is so big.

847
00:38:41,260 --> 00:38:42,660
When I was young, I also dreamed

848
00:38:42,940 --> 00:38:45,580
