851
00:38:49,420 --> 00:38:50,540
You're my son.

852
00:38:50,820 --> 00:38:51,700
I understand you.

853
00:38:53,140 --> 00:38:53,980
Besides,

854
00:38:54,220 --> 00:38:55,540
