855
00:38:56,260 --> 00:38:58,300
You have the right to choose your way.

856
00:38:58,620 --> 00:38:59,740
But remember one thing.

857
00:39:00,140 --> 00:39:02,820
If one day you can't survive out there,

858
00:39:03,220 --> 00:39:04,140
